    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed all 13 ASME V&V 40 factors. Seven factors were assessed; all achieved levels fall below required levels for MRL 5. Six factors remain not-assessed epistemic gaps. Despite these gaps, the assessment is accepted for submission as a documented credibility evidence package, with the understanding that additional evidence must be generated prior to regulatory submission. The stale rheological input dataset (dataVintage 2018) was not flagged as requiring re-validation following the January 2026 model revision.",
